          "locale": {
            "en-us": {
              "bullet_points": "•  Features hero cuffs, plasma ball shooter, anti-toxic power boots and tank arm\r\n•  Decorated chest piece\r\n•  Highly flexible and poseable elements\r\n•  Includes unique code worth 200 game points for LEGO Hero Factory BREAKOUT game\r\n•  Plasma ball shooter really shoots!\r\n•  Battle with the dangerous 6201 TOXIC REAPA\r\n•  Combine with 6201 TOXIC REAPA for an even bigger model!\r\n•  Stands over 6” (17cm) tall!",
              "display_title": "EVO",
              "description": "“Attention, EVO! The evil villains have broken out of the Hero Factory and we have to recapture them, fast! We’ve equipped you with a powerful plasma shooter, anti-toxic power boots and tank arm, so you have everything you need to cuff them and put them back behind bars where they belong!”",
              "title": "EVO",
              "headline": "Battle the villains with EVO’s tough anti-toxic armour!",
              "tags": []
            },
            "ko-kr": {
              "display_title": "에보",
              "description": "“주목하라! 에보! 못된 악당들이 히어로 팩토리에서 탈출했다. 악당들을 빨리 잡아야 한다! 강력한 플라스마 슈터, 항독성 신발, 탱크 암으로 무장하고 있으므로 녀석들을 제자리에 돌려놓는 데 필요한 모든 걸다 갖추고 있는 셈이다!”",
              "title": "에보",
